{"tid":374813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[單車撚] 覺唔覺係香港踩roadbike係玩鳩自己","createTime":"2017-08-26T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T22:03:40.000Z","uid":72187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"baf3bd0f0fad85402079cdc897d8972abd7cd7aa","tid":374813,"uid":72187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"單車徑本身鋪唔平 <br />\n一段幾個駁位 踩小小又行人路 落車推多過踩<br />\n馬路又多渠蓋"},{"pid":"1ec55d7b783f94d44cb0f29b804c1bfcb4122917","tid":374813,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"都好過踩出馬路玩命"},{"pid":"bfbc337ebb9c493367ead2d309cd8a6667c18301","tid":374813,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都好過踩出馬路玩命</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> roadbike踩單車徑先係玩命，直接縮短踩單車生涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1）單車徑勁多新手/唔熟單車既人/小朋友會突然靠左靠右，煞車，完全估佢唔到，之後你反應慢d就炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）香港單車徑斷斷續續，好多駁位，roadbike上落得駁位多，鈴都變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3）香港單車徑經常有路障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比行人過單車徑，個路障側邊仲有雨水渠蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> roadbike會zip落去之後炒車，渠蓋同路障之間只有半米闊，仲難過私家車泊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）單車徑超多行人，roadbike要就住慢行，真係少d平衡力都跌落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論，roadbike行馬路意外少，但一出事就死人，行單車徑一日起碼換幾次內軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比雨水渠zip爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好易有意外搞到你斷手斷腳、同線使用者極危險<br />\n<br />\n建議考左車牌，再用roadbike踏馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6cabab557eb45f8863c21791b2355c1b5514db","tid":374813,"uid":72187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T21:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都好過踩出馬路玩命</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> roadbike踩單車徑先係玩命，直接縮短踩單車生涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1）單車徑勁多新手/唔熟單車既人/小朋友會突然靠左靠右，煞車，完全估佢唔到，之後你反應慢d就炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）香港單車徑斷斷續續，好多駁位，roadbike上落得駁位多，鈴都變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3）香港單車徑經常有路障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比行人過單車徑，個路障側邊仲有雨水渠蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> roadbike會zip落去之後炒車，渠蓋同路障之間只有半米闊，仲難過私家車泊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）單車徑超多行人，roadbike要就住慢行，真係少d平衡力都跌落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論，roadbike行馬路意外少，但一出事就死人，行單車徑一日起碼換幾次內軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比雨水渠zip爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好易有意外搞到你斷手斷腳、同線使用者極危險<br />\n<br />\n建議考左車牌，再用roadbike踏馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a0eaf6f2a6e191f1beeb63b0569f88c0f0db26","tid":374813,"uid":21194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T21:10:16.000Z","msg":"踩左幾年轉左玩山車嚕<br />\n炒車最多擦損手腳"},{"pid":"248f97172336a12db6c63d7127ef120962ea187a","tid":374813,"uid":72277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T21:13:31.000Z","msg":"我都係rb撚<br />\n假日既吐公難度應該高過環法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議用車牌登記單車牌先俾出馬路踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604564de63fa5d551f334ffb2311d86d84a68b79","tid":374813,"uid":36720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T22:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係rb撚<br />\n假日既吐公難度應該高過環法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議用車牌登記單車牌先俾出馬路踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多jojo 會突然停低做road block <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲會有好多急轉彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}